_sText: I hope u have fun with this map ;-)

This is my first jail map. There are a couple of secret passages and stuff... And a pool.. I also like the control room, from where you can see all the cells and control the cell doors and other doors. But the map is definitely not finish yet. I have only tested it with bots.. And they are not very good at jail maps.. :P But I would like to see it used on a jail server.. So if anyone uses it, please let me no, because I would like to see it in action. :)

The map is basically 32 players, but there are a lot more spawnpoints in case you want to play with lots of terrorists and few counter-terrorists or the other way round.


Update 2009-03-18: Added some stuff to the map. Check it out!

Hi! Long time no C. :D
I got this job to make a map to a friends server. :P
but, suddently he changed his mind and told me he wasn't gonna make a ba_jail server anyway. :(
By then, I was already finished with my map, so I disided I'd put it on FPSB beacuse I don't like wasting my time in nothing at all.
So I wasted a little more of my time to write this extremly long readme note and publishing my map, just for fun.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
The map contains:

-Cells.
-A big play arena.
-Healing. (Not spiritual)
-Pool.
-Showers.
-Soccer field.
-Playground.
-Vents.
-Race track.
-Multifuncional dooropener. (1 to open, 1 to close :D)

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Effects and Stuff like that!!!

-HDR (that looks good at night. :O)
-Nice light effects in cells.
-Areaportals.
-Top glass windows.
-3D skybox. (got 2 <3 it!!!)
-Advanced soccer settings. (automaticly change the server settinge to soccer settings.)
-Custom skybox.

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Hope U like it :D

PS: U better like it!!!



-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Some People don't like HDR. (like me :S)

this is how to turn it off:

write: "mat_hdr_enable 0" in console.

the hdr isn't modifyed correctly when u download the map.
this is the settings u have to us on the server:

1.) write: "buildcubamaps" in console.
2.) write: "mat_hdr_enable 0" in console.
3.) write: "buildcubemaps" in console again.
4.) exit the server.
5.) write "mat_hdr_enable 1" in console.
6,) open the server and the HDR will work properly.


if u didn't get the part on the top... just turn the HDR off :P


------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

I think the map name explains itself.

The map has :
~40 Spawns (like all my maps) Ct=20 T=20
~12 Cells
~Guns Available : Ak47, M4A1, M249 (Hidden), Elites, Deagle, Flash bangs, Grenades, Smoke Grenades, Awps, Scouts and full armor.
~3 Hidden Rooms
~Much detail
~Football pitch
~Sea (instead of pool)
~Cage (ofc)
~A clock ?! Never seen that befure have you ? =)
~1 Secret room

NOTE : Last two screen shots are missing some things from the "newer" version but it gives you the idea befure you get to play the actual map.
__________________________________________________________
Update :
~It is now possible to climb onto the showers in the shower room. (No need fur another player to boost.)
~Added new song instead of the old one.
~Fixed armory bug when getting additional armor.
~Added lasers to new dual elites (with infinite ammo) and to the m249 that is hidden.
~Fixed football pitch. The ball can no longer leave the pitch.
~Fixed the water.
~Redid the secret room to get onto the walls using the secret door from cell #1.
~Added a ladder next to the cage.
